{"tid":1197983,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"領事保護權一問","createTime":"2019-06-10T06:10:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T06:20:19.000Z","uid":58131,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8e2952ecc6c10ca67bb00d5057177af836f10546","tid":1197983,"uid":58131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T06:10:18.000Z","msg":"我想問下係有外國護照，而冇中國籍，喺香港係咪可以擁有領事保護權？如果有嘅話又可以點樣行使？<br />\n<br />\n之前追過post，有巴打講過問過入境處，話如果父母有外國國籍，係外國出生既子女，並不會有中國國籍，所以子女應只有外國戶籍而非中國籍，而作為外國公民應該享有領事保護權。但有一種講法，話香港人係香港不得擁有領事保護，加上持有特衰，想問下邊一隻先係正確說法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：加籍港人又持有特衰"},{"pid":"28c3e661b205ce01e6d9c7eba06c386ae6b7b357","tid":1197983,"uid":5220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T06:12:57.000Z","msg":"你要出境然後用外國護照再入境香港"},{"pid":"c8f150d00f4fda0363cd866f30952c8ef6973f92","tid":1197983,"uid":33028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"28c3e661b205ce01e6d9c7eba06c386ae6b7b357","tid":1197983,"uid":5220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T06:12:57.000Z","msg":"你要出境然後用外國護照再入境香港"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T06:14:25.000Z","msg":"要申報國籍變更"},{"pid":"7d855765f46e86b9a41cc3a4bacc5d831093ff03","tid":1197983,"uid":5220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c8f150d00f4fda0363cd866f30952c8ef6973f92","tid":1197983,"uid":33028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"28c3e661b205ce01e6d9c7eba06c386ae6b7b357","tid":1197983,"uid":5220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T06:12:57.000Z","msg":"你要出境然後用外國護照再入境香港"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T06:14:25.000Z","msg":"要申報國籍變更"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T06:16:48.000Z","msg":"係喎，睇漏左<br />\n有特衰即係中國人了<br />\n要放棄中國國籍先"},{"pid":"41af780125c1e421cee752718a85cb1a525f560f","tid":1197983,"uid":58131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d855765f46e86b9a41cc3a4bacc5d831093ff03","tid":1197983,"uid":5220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"p